## Data Types

- `int` â†’ whole numbers  
- `double` â†’ decimal numbers  
- `String` â†’ text  
- `bool` â†’ true/false  
- `dynamic` â†’ flexible type  

```dart
int age = 20;
double price = 99.99;
String city = "Dhaka";
bool isActive = true;
dynamic anything = "Hello"; 
anything = 123; // âœ… Allowed

## String Interpolation

```dart
String name = "Samir";
int age = 20;

print("My name is $name and I am $age years old.");
print("Next year I will be ${age + 1} years old.");
```
